        <trans-unit id="105" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>As with all applications that must be localized (released in different versions for different languages and cultures), any strings that are displayed to the user should not be put directly in code, but rather stored in a resource file.</source>
        </trans-unit>
